data.description: You just found the home you have been searching for. Checkout this 3-bedroom 2 bath one story home with finished bonus room over garage. Located on a corner lot. This home also features a galley style kitchen with granite countertops, soft close drawers and pull-out spice racks. Large master bedroom with his/her walk-in closets, double vanities, jetted bathtub and separate shower. There is a formal dining room for entertaining guests and an inground pool with a pool house. Timed irrigation system and walk-in attic storage. Don't miss out on this beautiful residence.
